snippet.title: Outcast - A New Beginning | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Outcast - A New Beginning is coming soon to PC, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series S|X.

The cult classic returns! Cutter Slade has been resurrected by the mighty Yods in order to join forces with the Talan people. The inhabitants of the paradisiac planet Adelpha are blissfully unaware of the army of invading soldiers. But that’s all about to change…

- Pre-Order Here -
Steam: https://thqn.net/outcast2-steam
PSN: https://thqn.net/outcast2-psn
Xbox: https://thqn.net/outcast2-xbox

- Links & Info -
Website: https://www.outcast2.com
